SELECT_x000D_
DISTINCT_x000D_
CAST(B.MSTR_ID AS VARCHAR(15))AS MSTR_ID,_x000D_
C.EFFECTIVEDATE AS EFF_DT,_x000D_
SUBSTR(A.FIELDNAME,14,3) AS CVG_TYP,_x000D_
TRIM(LEADING '0' FROM (SUBSTR(A.FIELDNAME,17,3))) AS CVG_SEQ_NUM,_x000D_
SUBSTR(A.FIELDNAME,4,10) AS RT_TYP,_x000D_
A.FLOATVALUE AS RT_VAL_x000D_
FROM _x000D_
$$DBOWNER.ASSCHEDULEDVALUATIONFIELD A_x000D_
LEFT OUTER JOIN _x000D_
(SELECT _x000D_
SCHEDULEDVALUATIONGUID, _x000D_
TEXTVALUE AS MSTR_ID _x000D_
 FROM _x000D_
$$DBOWNER.ASSCHEDULEDVALUATIONFIELD_x000D_
WHERE FIELDNAME='PolicyNumber' _x000D_
) B_x000D_
ON A.SCHEDULEDVALUATIONGUID=B.SCHEDULEDVALUATIONGUID_x000D_
JOIN $$DBOWNER.ASSCHEDULEDVALUATION C_x000D_
ON A.SCHEDULEDVALUATIONGUID=C.SCHEDULEDVALUATIONGUID _x000D_
JOIN $$DBOWNER.ASSYSTEMDATE D_x000D_
ON C.ACTIVEDATE=D.PREVIOUSSYSTEMDATE_x000D_
WHERE _x000D_
FIELDNAME LIKE 'CVG%' _x000D_
AND _x000D_
D.CURRENTINDICATOR = 'Y' _x000D_
AND _x000D_
B.MSTR_ID IS NOT NULL_x000D_
 ORDER BY MSTR_ID,EFF_DT,CVG_TYP,CVG_SEQ_NUM,RT_TYP ASC
